Sentencas: Oxygen-ion transport property greatly affects the electro-catalytic activity of a cathode material in the solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Ca3Co2O6-Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 composite cathode material for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In this work, to enhance the electrochemical activity of hexagonal Ca(3)Co(2)0(6) cathode, fast ion-conductor Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 is introduced as the second phase, and thus a binary composite is developed, expressed as (l-x)Ca3Co2O6/xCe(0.8)Sm(0.2)O(1.9) in nominal form.
Titulo: Ca3Co2O6-Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 composite cathode material for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The composites are prepared by one-pot method and X-ray diffraction results reveal that these compositional phases are highly compatible.
Titulo: Ca3Co2O6-Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 composite cathode material for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Analysis of X-ray photoelectron spectroscopy indicates the existence of Co3+ and Co2+ mixed valences in the composites.
Titulo: Ca3Co2O6-Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 composite cathode material for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Compared with single-phase Ca3Co2O6, thermal expansion coefficient of the composite is favorably low and matches better with the electrolyte of solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Ca3Co2O6-Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 composite cathode material for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Test of electrical conductivity shows that the composites are comparable to the pure Ca3Co2O6 in charge transport capacity.
Titulo: Ca3Co2O6-Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 composite cathode material for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Electrochemical measurements indicate that the x=0.5 composite cathode exhibit the lowest area specific resistance and produces the maximum power density.
Titulo: Ca3Co2O6-Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 composite cathode material for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In the electrolyte-supported single cell along with Ni-SDC cermet as anode and pure H-2 gas as fuel, power density peak of 680 mWcm(-2) is achieved from the x = 0.5 composite cathode at 800 degrees C. (c) 2018
Titulo: Ca3Co2O6-Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 composite cathode material for solid oxide fuel cells
